		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">The scope of the Tianqi-reported data allows for a facility-levelanalysis of the material, water, and energy needed to produce 1 tonneof LiOH•H2O or Li2CO3 from spodumene concentrate (Table 5). A significantamount of coal is used for process heat, split between use as fuelfor an acid-roasting kiln and for steam production. Tianqi reports that ituses 12 tonnes of steam per tonne of LiOH•H2O produced and 16.5tonnes of steam per tonne of Li2CO3 produced. Note also that Na2SO4 is produced as a by-product of this process. Wedetermined the quantity of the by-product but did not allocate anyburdens to it.</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">根据天齐公司报告的数据范围，可以对利用锂精矿生产 1 吨 LiOH-H2O 或 Li2CO3 所需的材料、水和能源进行设施级分析。煤炭用于工艺加热，分为用作酸焙烧窑的燃料和蒸汽生产。据天齐公司报告，每生产一吨 LiOH-H2O 需用 12 吨蒸汽，每生产一吨 Li2CO3 需用 16.5 吨蒸汽。还要注意的是，Na2SO4 是这一过程的副产品。我们确定了副产品的数量，但没有为其分配任何负担。</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The battery grade lithium hydroxide monohydrate produced through the lithium sulfate process is used predominantly in the manufacture of lithium-ion batteries. Such batteries are integral to a variety of applications, including electric vehicles, portable electronics, and energy storage systems.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">通过硫酸锂法生产的电池级单水氢氧化锂主要用于锂离子电池的制造。这类电池是多种应用的核心部分，包括电动汽车、便携式电子设备和能量储存系统。</technologicalApplicability>
